<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<% const PAGE = 'finish'; %>

<head>
    <%- include('includes/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/prism-themes@1.3.0/themes/prism-vs.min.css">
</head>

<body class="sk-bg-gray">
    <%- include('includes/navbar') %>
    <div class="container sk-my-8">
        <%- include('includes/steps', { PAGE }) %>
        <div class="card sk-center">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="h4 text-center sk-mb-4">编辑完成！</h2>
                <div class="text-justify ce-card-docs">
                    <p>您已经成功完成了一份 Clash 配置文件的编辑！您可以下载您的配置文件、预览您的配置文件，或者清除 Clash Editor 保存在您浏览器中的数据。</p>
                    <p>请注意保管好您的配置文件、不要轻易泄漏！</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card sk-center sk-mt-4">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <a href="#" id="finish-download-yaml" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">下载 YAML 配置文件</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <a href="#" id="finish-download-json" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">下载 JSON 配置文件</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br>
                <button id="finish-preview-yaml" class="btn btn-info btn-block">预览 Clash 配置文件</button>
                <p class="sk-mb-0"><small>如果您当前配置文件比较大，则并不建议在浏览器中预览。</small></p>
                <br>
                <button id="finish-clean-cache" class="btn btn-secondary btn-block">清理浏览器缓存</button>
                <p class="sk-mb-0"><small>您当前配置文件的 General、Proxy、Proxy Group、Rule 都存储在浏览器本地，您下次编辑时会自动还原。如果您不希望浏览器继续存储这些信息，请使用「清理浏览器缓存」。</small></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <pre class="sk-mt-4"><code id="finish-yml" class="language-yaml"></code></pre>
    </div>
    <%- include('includes/modal') %>
    <%- include('includes/footer') %>
    <script>
        window.Prism = window.Prism || {};
        window.Prism.manual = true;
    </script>
    <%- include('includes/footer_for_editor') %>
    <script src="/js/<%= PAGE %>.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
